title: Worst Date Wednesday: You're going to visit a GUY?
description: Stephanie tells us about a second date she went on that she only really went on to give the guy a second shot.  Well he blew it.  He brought up politics, talked about how he googled and found out tons of info about her, and then showed jealous qualities when she said she was going out of town to visit a guy friend.
